'S e baile ann an [[Siorrachd Aonghais]] a tha ann an '''Druiminn''' ([[Beurla]]: ''Drymen''). <ref>[http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/vli/language/gaelic/pdfs/placenamesC-E.pdf Iain Mac an Tailleir], "Ainmean-Àite", duilleag 41, Pàrlamaid na h-Alba</ref> Tha am baile gu lèir suidhichte ann am [[Pàirc Loch Laomainn agus Nan Tròsaichean]]. 'S e seo na [[Co-chomharran an Domhain|co-chomharran]] aige: 56° 3′ 53.86″ Tuath agus  4° 27′ 3.85″ Iar. 

Anns a' bhliadhna 2004 bha 760 duine a' fuireach an seo. <ref> [http://www.gro-scotland.gov.uk/statistics/publications-and-data/settlements-and-localities/mid-2004-population-estimates-for-settlements-in-scotland.html Mid-2004 Population Estimates for Settlements in Scotland]</ref>

Tha an taigh-seinnse “''The Clachan''” ag ràdh gur esan an taigh-seinnse as sine ann an Alba. Tha ceanglaichean aige leis an teaghlach [[Rob Ruadh MacGriogair|Rob Ruadh]].

